两组的位置参数并不相同，因此使用Mood方法检验结果并不合理

mood.test(a,b)
## 
##  Mood two-sample test of scale
## 
## data:  a and b
## Z = 0.63418, p-value = 0.526
## alternative hypothesis: two.sided

Mood检验没有否定原假设,但是由于两组的位置参数并不相同，检验结果并不可靠

varrank=function(x,y,nx=3,ny=3){
  n_x=length(x)%/%nx
  n_y=length(y)%/%ny
  x=sample(x,length(x))
  y=sample(y,length(y))
  x_var=c()
  y_var=c()
  for (i in 1:n_x) {
    temp=x[((i-1)*nx+1):(i*nx)]
    x_var=c(x_var,var(temp))
  }
  for (i in 1:n_y) {
    temp=y[((i-1)*ny+1):(i*ny)]
    y_var=c(y_var,var(temp))
  }
  ans=list(n_x=n_x,n_y=n_y,x_var=x_var,y_var=y_var)
  return(ans)
}

ans=varrank(a,b)
wilcox.test(ans$x_var,ans$y_var)
## 
##  Wilcoxon rank sum exact test
## 
## data:  ans$x_var and ans$y_var
## W = 4, p-value = 0.1905
## alternative hypothesis: true location shift is not equal to 0
ans=varrank(a,b)
wilcox.test(ans$x_var,ans$y_var)
##

## 
## data:  ans$x_var and ans$y_var
## W = 3, p-value = 0.1111
## alternative hypothesis: true location shift is not equal to 0
ans=varrank(a,b)

可以看到，随着每次的分组不同，结果差异极大

2.2

a=c(83,64,67,62,70)
b=c(85,81,80,78)
c=c(88,89,79,90,95)

n=sort(c(a,b,c))
r_a=c()
for (i in a) {
  r_a=c(r_a,which(n==i))
}
r_b=c()
for (i in b) {
  r_b=c(r_b,which(n==i))
}
r_c=c()
for (i in c) {
  r_c=c(r_c,which(n==i))
}
cat("a:",r_a,'\n')
## a: 9 2 3 1 4
cat("b:",r_b,'\n')
## b: 10 8 7 5
cat("c:",r_c,'\n')
## c: 11 12 6 13 14
sst=length(a)*(mean(r_a)-(length(n)+1)/2)^2+
  length(b)*(mean(r_b)-(length(n)+1)/2)^2+
  length(c)*(mean(r_c)-(length(n)+1)/2)^2

cat("sst=",sst,'\n')
## sst= 136.9
mst=length(n)*(length(n)+1)/12
cat("mst=",mst,'\n')
## mst= 17.5
H=sst/mst
cat("H=",H,'\n')
## H= 7.822857
cat(qchisq(0.95,3-1))
## 5.991465

\(H=7.82>\chi^2_{1-0.05}(3-1)=5.99\)

因此拒绝原假设，认为三组数据存在差别

3.1

dunn=function(x,alpha=0.05){
  cat("alpha=",alpha,'\n')
  n=c()
  for (i in 1:length(x)) {
    n=c(n,unlist(x[i]))
  }
  n=sort(n)
  len=length(n)
  r_x=list()
  for (i in 1:length(x)) {
    temp=c()
    for (j in unlist(x[i])) {
      temp=c(temp,which(n==j)[1])
    }
    r_x=append(r_x,list(temp))
  }
  for (i in 1:(length(x)-1)){
    for (j in (i+1):length(x)){
      a=unlist(r_x[i])
      b=unlist(r_x[j])
      seij=sqrt(len*(len+1)/12*(1/length(a)+1/length(b)))
      dij=abs(mean(a)-mean(b))/seij
      z=qnorm(1-alpha)
      if(dij<z){
        cat(i,'-',j,'  SE=',seij,'  dij=',dij,'   z=',z,'\n',sep = '')
      }
      else{
        cat(i,'-',j,'  SE=',seij,'  dij=',dij,'*  z=',z,'\n',sep = '')
      }
    }
  }
}
x=list(c(3.7,3.7,3.0,3.9,2.7),c(7.3,5.2,5.3,5.7,6.5),c(9.0,4.9,7.1,8.7))
dunn(x)
## alpha= 0.05 
## 1-2  SE=2.645751  dij=2.418973*  z=1.644854
## 1-3  SE=2.806243  dij=2.922056*  z=1.644854
## 2-3  SE=2.806243  dij=0.641427   z=1.644854

认为1、2组，1、3组之间存在差别
